es with the victim and reconstructs the sequence of events. Since Chi-yue met restaurant boss Wong Mik-kei, the duo are no longer “spectators”. Perpetrators at large are killed one after another. Chi-yue covertly challenges some serial killer on several occasions, and their true identity is gradually uncovered. Chi-yue realizes the two of them have conflicting standpoints even though they are like-minded, causing her to face the conundrum of making life choices. In the meantime, Mik-hei astonishingly makes some decision for her.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"234218","season":1,"vote_average":9,"vote_count":1},"modified":"2025-08-07T21:46:16.000Z","cast":["Châu Bách Hào","Vương Mẫn Dịch","Liên Thi Nhã","Ngô Nhược Hy","Mã Quán Đông","Joey Law","Wong Ka-Lok","Nicole Wan See Pui","Brian Tse Tung Man","Hero Yuen","Janice Ting","Joan Lee Wing-Yee","David Do","Daniel Chau","Viên Vỹ Hào"],"director":["Yip Chun Fai"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Châu Bách Hào","name_vi":"Châu Bách Hào","name_original":"Pakho Chau","tmdb_id":1123831,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yhCcx2GXlIhrppiVW6vkbmIiNRX.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1123831"},{"name":"Vương Mẫn Dịch","name_vi":"Vương Mẫn Dịch","name_original":"Venus Wong Man-Yik","tmdb_id":937492,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ySEEfNsEIFj8mPb84lnyVVbfSB0.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/937492"},{"name":"Liên Thi Nhã","name_vi":"Liên Thi Nhã","name_original":"Shiga Lin Si-Nga","tmdb_id":590921,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/S4z2qMN1nd06K0sRTQkd3gz4hq.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/590921"},{"name":"Ngô Nhược Hy","name_vi":"Ngô Nhược Hy","name_original":"Jinny Ng","tmdb_id":1263928,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3nOeXDNO9oN4WgcJKZ2pBQdcrG5.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1263928"},{"name":"Mã Quán Đông","name_vi":"Mã Quán Đông","name_original":"Mark Ma","tmdb_id":2671663,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b2O04lOj